jobs.title: Tetra Pak - Service Management Consultant
jobs.description: Tetra Pak is revolutionizing its digital landscape with the Next Chapter Systems Platform (NCSP) Program, implementing SAP S/4 HANA to modernize services. Are you ready to take on a key role in shaping this transformation? You will implement SAP best practices and standards while collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality solutions. If you are passionate about optimizing processes and driving innovation, this is your chance to be part of something transformative!

jobs.title: Senior Full Stack Developer
jobs.description: We're looking for a senior Full Stack Developer to join our dynamic team developing cutting-edge web applications. The ideal candidate has experience with both frontend and backend technologies, can architect complex systems, and has a passion for clean, maintainable code. This role offers the opportunity to work with the latest technologies in a collaborative team environment.
